\newlabel{fig:spread_levels}{{5.3}{23}{Spread levels with $\pm 1\sigma $ and $\pm 2\sigma $ bands for each cointegrated pair over the in-sample period (January 2019 -- December 2023). The spread is defined as $S_t = \ln P^y_t - \hat {\beta }\ln P^x_t - \hat {\alpha }$. (a)~KO/PEP; (b)~GS/MS; (c)~DAL/UAL}{figure.5.3}{}}
