\newlabel{fig:spread_zscores}{{5.4}{24}{Rolling $z$-scores (60-day window) for the two cointegrated pairs over the in-sample period (January 2019 -- December 2023). Dotted lines mark the $\pm 2\sigma $ entry thresholds. The $z$-score at the end of the training window feeds directly into the OU-implied return estimation. (a)~KO/PEP; (b)~GS/MS; (c)~DAL/UAL}{figure.5.4}{}}
